# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# Localization message writes require ADMIN and an authenticated session.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionCookie = paste-technical-interview-demo-session-here
@localizationMessageId = 1
@writeLocalizationMessageId = 0
@demoMessageKey = info.book.created.demo-change-me-if-rerunning

### LocalizationMessageController - list localization messages with pagination and sorting
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages?page=0&size=5&sort=messageKey,asc&sort=language,asc
Accept: application/json

### LocalizationMessageController - get a seeded message by key and language and capture its id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages/key/error.book.not_found/lang/en
Accept: application/json

> {%
if (response.status === 200) {
  client.global.set("localizationMessageId", String(response.body.id));
}
%}

### LocalizationMessageController - get localization message by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages/{{localizationMessageId}}
Accept: application/json

### LocalizationMessageController - list messages for one language
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages/language/es
Accept: application/json

### LocalizationMessageController - create localization message (ADMIN + authenticated session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "messageKey": "{{demoMessageKey}}",
  "language": "fr",
  "messageText": "Le livre a ete cree.",
  "description": "French success message for demo requests."
}
> {%
if (response.status === 201) {
  client.global.set("writeLocalizationMessageId", String(response.body.id));
}
%}

### LocalizationMessageController - update the localization message created above (run create first)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages/{{writeLocalizationMessageId}}
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "messageKey": "{{demoMessageKey}}",
  "language": "fr",
  "messageText": "Le livre a ete cree avec succes.",
  "description": "Updated French success message for demo requests."
}

### LocalizationMessageController - delete the localization message created above (run create first)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/localization-messages/{{writeLocalizationMessageId}}
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
